This paper deals with the task of arbitrary style transfer, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI). The proposed approach involves the use of deep neural networks with an attention mechanism, which is a popular technique in deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the processing of portrait images, which is a common topic in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
